# This document was written at the beginning of the development process prior. It includes the initial steps conceptualized by the Scrum Master(s)
Steps:
1. Set up a Trello or google doc
2. Identify the 4x4 area needed
3. Decide whether fixed position or moving position
4. Detect a red standard sized brick on the floor
  a. Gather and label images of the brick
  b. Decide which payload camera to use
